---
title: Caramelized Apple Melts with a Honey Dijon Arugula Salad
description: Sure, a classic white bread and American cheese melt hits the spot every now and then—but try one bite of this sweet and savory sandwich, and you just might want to add it to your weeknight repertoire. Sourdough bread slices are swiped with Dijon mustard, then layered with mozzarella and a caramelized apple filling. They’re griddled in butter until perfectly golden brown and melty and paired with arugula, dried cranberries, and sunflower seeds tossed in a tangy Honey Dijon Dressing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caramelized-apple-melts-f2ba7dbc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/caramelized-apple-melts-608026064b9f7341ac2522a0-ea635fb2.pdf
